name: The Twins
description: '''Brooke Kelaart''' and '''Ellie Kelaart''' are an [[Australia]]n [[Electronic dance music|EDM]], [[electro house]] and [[progressive house]] duo, better known by their stage name '''The Twins'''. After signing with [[Sony/ATV Music Publishing]] at 18 years of age, the sisters pursued careers as songwriting partners and, in 2008, they signed with [[Fredrik Olsson (music executive)|Fredrik Olsson]] and his Swedish music publishing company [[Razor Boy Music Publishing]].
